    "en": {
      "title": "It takes 14 - 16 days to get back to normal",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "According to the Public Utilities Commission of Sri Lanka, it will take about 14-16 days to complete the repair work of the first generator that has broken down at Nuraicholai Thermal Power Station.",
        "According to this, today's power cut will be implemented for one hour and twenty minutes and the power cut will be extended from tomorrow (16).",
        "It is noteworthy that due to this emergency that occurred this morning (15), the Nuraicholai thermal power station has not been able to contribute fully to the national power supply. (R)"
      ],
